org.apache.ignite.stream.jms11

Interface MessageTransformer<T extends javax.jms.Message,K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of JMS Message.
    K - The type of the cache key.
    V - The type of the cache value.

    public interface MessageTransformer<T extends javax.jms.Message,K,V>
    Implement this interface to transform from a Message to a set of cache entries in the form of a Map.

        Transformation function.
        Parameters:
        message - The message received from the JMS broker.
